trans-unit.source: Represents a range of dates in a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et datoområde i en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: CalendarDateRange objects are primarily used by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection> to specify a range of dates that are not selectable in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.
trans-unit.target: CalendarDateRange objektene brukes hovedsakelig av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection>til å angi datoområdet for som er ikke velges i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CalendarDateRange"></xref> class with a range of dates.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CalendarDateRange"> </xref> klassen med et område med datoer.
